p: \b\pn, the ratings from the last episode are out the roof!
\bIf we want to retain viewers, we have to have an exciting second episode.
\bAnd guess what- not only was there a rare Pokemon reported here...
\bBut that rare Pokemon is a Delta Species!
\bThat's right! Delta Pokemon are the rarest of the rare!
\bIf we can find it, we'll be the most popular channel on TV!
\bAgain, we've got helicopters everywhere in the area.
\bAll you need to do is to use your skills as a trainer to find that Delta!
\bIf you want to capture it, you can, just get us some footage!
\bTalk to my associate if you need a tip!
\bWe need footage of you battling, so get going!
\bYou were fantastic, \pn. We got the whole thing recorded!
\bWe'll give you a call on your Pokegear when we're ready to film again, OK?
\rI don't think this is going to be like finding the Axew.
\rI've seen some of the sand rustling, but whatever is under the surface never stops moving!
\rYou might need to chase it and catch it to encounter it!
\b\pn! We got that on tape! Come back over here!
